text: Prinsha Shrestha (born September 11, 1992) in Kathmandu, Nepal is a Nepali Model and the title winner of Miss Earth Nepal 2014. She was dethroned in April 5, 2015 cause of her participation in Miss Eco Queen 2015 wearing Miss Earth official sash. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Beauty pageant winners Category:People from Kathmandu Category:Nepalese models
